# 詞: 睇怕

1. 睇怕聽日都會落雨，記得帶遮啦。(It looks like it's going to rain tomorrow, remember to bring an umbrella.)

2. 佢成日遲到，睇怕今次都唔會準時嚟。(He's always late, I'm afraid he won't be on time this time either.)

3. 呢間餐廳咁多人排隊，睇怕要等成個鐘先有位。(There's such a long queue at this restaurant, it looks like we'll have to wait for an hour to get a seat.)

4. 阿明最近日日OT，睇怕佢好快就會病倒。(Ah Ming has been working overtime every day lately, I'm afraid he'll fall sick soon.)

5. 睇怕呢單生意都係做唔成，對方根本冇誠意。(It looks like this deal won't go through, the other party doesn't seem to be serious at all.)

6. 股市咁波動，睇怕今年都係蝕錢收場。(The stock market is so volatile, I'm afraid we'll end up losing money this year.)

7. 佢哋兩個成日嗌交，睇怕好快就會分手。(They argue all the time, I'm afraid they'll break up soon.)

8. 呢隻股票連跌三日，睇怕仲會再跌。(This stock has been falling for three days straight, it looks like it will continue to drop.)

9. 睇怕呢次考試都係唔合格，完全冇溫過書。(I'm afraid I'll fail this exam, I haven't studied at all.)

10. 天氣預報話有颱風，睇怕聽日要停課。(The weather forecast says there's a typhoon, it looks like classes will be suspended tomorrow.) [end of text]


